WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.136
Arrgh! This desert be hot! I've walked forever and still no clue. This old compass is spinning

00:07.136 --> 00:11.653
like mad. Where do I go now? Maybe this map's just a big joke.

00:11.653 --> 00:15.866
"You seem lost, stranger. What are you looking for?"

00:15.866 --> 00:19.464
A clue, a sign, something about treasure.

00:19.464 --> 00:27.747
"Then hear this—
 Where rivers five do flow with pride,
 A clue awaits, not far to hide."

00:27.747 --> 00:32.88
Rivers? Five of them? Aha! That’s Pakistan for sure!